odels behind claude when impl was gpt\", () => {\n    const candidates = [\n      { id: \"gpt-5.4\", reasoningEffort: null },         // same broad family as gpt-5.1\n      { id: \"claude-sonnet-4.6\", reasoningEffort: null }, // distinct family\n      { id: \"gpt-5-mini\", reasoningEffort: null },       // same broad family, different sub-family\n    ];\n    const result = orderCandidates(candidates, { kind: \"review\" }, \"gpt-5.1\");\n    const claudeIdx = result.findIndex((c) => c.id === \"claude-sonnet-4.6\");\n    const gpt54Idx  = result.findIndex((c) => c.id === \"gpt-5.4\");\n    const miniIdx   = result.findIndex((c) => c.id === \"gpt-5-mini\");\n    assert.ok(claudeIdx < gpt54Idx,  \"claude-sonnet-4.6 must precede gpt-5.4\");\n    assert.ok(claudeIdx < miniIdx,   \"claude-sonnet-4.6 must precede gpt-5-mini\");\n  });\n});",
